{"type":"message","id":"98dcac52","parentId":"59744e9d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T03:50:45.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I got the news from Sina. Now let me compile a concise morning news briefing based on what I see:\n\nKey headlines from today (March 19, 2026):\n\n🌍 INTERNATIONAL:\n- Major escalation in Middle East: Iran-Israel conflict intensifying, with energy infrastructure attacks\n- US President Trump says he was \"not aware\" of Israel's attacks on Iranian energy facilities\n- A major turning point in the war, entering a \"crazy phase\"\n- Iran launching attacks on US-related energy facilities\n- Pentagon says war with Iran has cost over $11.3 billion so far\n- War approaching Hormuz, India faces gas supply risk\n- World Health Organization preparing for possible \"nuclear disaster\"\n\n💼 BUSINESS/FINANCE:\n- Stock market: Shanghai Composite down 0.95%, Shenzhen down 1.11%\n- Gold price drops sharply, falling below $4920 per ounce\n- Multiple banks withdrawing from personal \"gold trading\" business\n- Langdo (岚图) car company listed on Hong Kong Stock Exchange\n- Rural land contract extension: second round extended for another 30 years\n\n💻 TECH:\n- AI agents driving demand, major cloud providers collectively raising prices\n- Tencent 2025 revenue up 14%, new AI products investment to double\n- Apple CEO Tim Cook visits Chengdu\n- Agent technology driving cloud service price increases\n\nLet me compile this into a concise news briefing.","thinkingSignature":"de532053c72f656d99e25df2d2d0483369cea15dae965ff885b5732b621c44e5"},{"type":"text","text":"Based on the news I gathered, here's this morning's news briefing:\n\n---\n\n📰 **早间新闻简报** — 2026年3月19日 周四\n\n---\n\n**🌍 国际热点**\n\n- **中东局势急剧升级**：伊朗与以色列冲突进入\"疯狂阶段\"，能源设施遭连环袭击，五角大楼已为所谓\"核灾难\"做准备\n- **特朗普**：对以袭击伊朗能源设施\"毫不知情\"，美军方称对伊战争成本已超113亿美元\n- **霍尔木兹海峡告急**：战争逼近能源咽喉，印度天然气面临断供风险\n\n---\n\n**💼 财经要闻**\n\n- **A股震荡**：上证跌0.95%，深证跌1.11%\n- **黄金跳水**：金价失守4920美元/盎司，市民排队买金；至少13家银行退出个人炒金业务\n- **土地政策**：农村承包地二轮到期后再延长30年\n- **岚图上市**：央国企高端新能源车第一股登陆港交所\n\n---\n\n**💻 科技动态**\n\n- **AI驱动云服务涨价**：全球云计算巨头集体提价，Agent需求旺盛\n- **腾讯年报**：2025营收增长14%，今年AI新产品投入至少翻倍\n- **库克访华**：苹果高管现身成都，锚定中国供应链\n\n---\n\n早安！祝您有美好的一天 🎩"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":58136,"output":580,"cacheRead":36895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95611,"cost":{"input":0.0174408,"output":0.000696,"cacheRead":0.00110685,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019243649999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773892220641}}
